{"tid":1228014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［睇成本］超簡單摺花教學 — 在某些場合用的花","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T18:03:36.000Z","uid":227755,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"991ac4f8991b9b78acd477d3d5edbd14e03f24e1","tid":1228014,"uid":227755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，請多多指教<br />\n<br />\n成品是這樣的： <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ev3aYJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fev3aYJG.png&h=e544bc38&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不同場合可以用不同顏色，不過這次我覺得黑白是最適合的。<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n紙巾兩張（最好每張有兩層，多d無所謂）<br />\n釘書機<br />\n墨水筆<br />\n鐵線（短短的，用來扎麵包袋的都可以）<br />\n扣針🧷（optional）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGC3zie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGC3zie.png&h=9c0998b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 把紙巾疊起放齊，然後由一邊摺起，摺到風琴咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCf1kYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCf1kYt.png&h=abe36290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHs3ziN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHs3ziN.png&h=93c35f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後會變成咁樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GX2CDLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGX2CDLz.png&h=7a01080f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 用鐵線幫助紙巾中間位置，如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tXSsD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tXSsD8.png&h=d9e243d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd1a39302e95d169bd55a447c2923317264f4baa","tid":1228014,"uid":2156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e925a537f452b4771c97cc2cc7beb6c3e65ce08","tid":1228014,"uid":199344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"聽日就整朵送出去"},{"pid":"bf628457e57ba2dfb7c8e8ff6b69ef30b9cfddcc","tid":1228014,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"唔該兄弟"},{"pid":"090d804d5d426489fdd114b4d3591bae6ddba290","tid":1228014,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c93d66da7e40385ca4da26b38857300d53e95375","tid":1228014,"uid":227755,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"991ac4f8991b9b78acd477d3d5edbd14e03f24e1","tid":1228014,"uid":227755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，請多多指教<br />\n<br />\n成品是這樣的： <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ev3aYJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fev3aYJG.png&h=e544bc38&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不同場合可以用不同顏色，不過這次我覺得黑白是最適合的。<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n紙巾兩張（最好每張有兩層，多d無所謂）<br />\n釘書機<br />\n墨水筆<br />\n鐵線（短短的，用來扎麵包袋的都可以）<br />\n扣針🧷（optional）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGC3zie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGC3zie.png&h=9c0998b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 把紙巾疊起放齊，然後由一邊摺起，摺到風琴咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCf1kYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCf1kYt.png&h=abe36290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHs3ziN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHs3ziN.png&h=93c35f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後會變成咁樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GX2CDLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGX2CDLz.png&h=7a01080f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 用鐵線幫助紙巾中間位置，如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tXSsD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tXSsD8.png&h=d9e243d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"3. 然後用你的筆，在兩旁畫顏色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B1vYMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B1vYMe.png&h=b14bb729&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcYiocV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcYiocV.png&h=2d7569ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1P5NEB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1P5NEB.png&h=6119b528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 把每層紙輕輕地分離（要小心不要太用力）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHfpiMJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHfpiMJ.png&h=714aa2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOoBUj4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOoBUj4.png&h=4bcf9a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 之後幫佢整理一下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLoY7Fo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLoY7Fo.png&h=2058ad7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.用釘書機固定：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfnrw7i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmfnrw7i.png&h=4b5e9a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 搞掂！ 如果你需要，可以扣一個扣針<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzCnPUn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzCnPUn.png&h=3ae963c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完成！<br />\n係咪好簡單呢！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52ac351179f37e3ca2cedca75feabbd1b9a81a4","tid":1228014,"uid":105408,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55168d49c57f82a5420a8504f487eb6acc4e8de1","t